## Pipeline

1. **`/legacy-spec` or `/spec`** вЂ” `*.bundle.yaml` design v1 + testcase round 1. No `gen` / `codegen`.
2. **`/bqa-grill-docs`** вЂ” UI, acceptance, breadcrumb, delete rules.
3. **`/dev-grill-docs`** вЂ” portal-gen-ready spec (`base-docs/templates/spec.yaml`) + `tags`. Gate: `pnpm portal:gen:dry --spec <file>`.
4. **`/grill-with-docs`** вЂ” optional reconcile when BQAв†”Dev contradict.
5. **`/update-spec`** / **`/update-spec-legacy`** вЂ” controlled delta + `#update:*` (not full rewrite).
6. **`/prototype`** вЂ” only after dev grill dry-run passes.

